\n4--8 MK plasma in this AR is mostly in bursts lasting less than 30 minutes: at\nmost a third of the heating is steady for 30 minutes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 17 Nov 2022 23:17:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-04"}
